PreferredFunction.name: driver shutdown
PreferredFunction.Reason: When drivers call NtShutdownSystem directly, the registry can be corrupted if there are other threads writing to it at the time of shutdown. Other unsaved user-mode data is also lost

PreferredFunction.name: KeQueryTickCount
PreferredFunction.Reason: GetTickCount overflows roughly every 49 days. Code that does not take that into account can loop indefinitely. KeQueryTickCount operates on 64 bit values and does not have that problem
